{{Vuelta a Venezuela}}
{{DEFAULTSORT:2007 Vuelta A Venezuela}} [[Category:Vuelta a Venezuela]] [[Category:2007 in road cycling|Venezuela]] [[Category:2007 in Venezuelan sport|Vuelta Venezuela]]

The 49th [[Cuban National Series]] was won by [[Industriales]] over [[Villa Clara (baseball)|Villa Clara]]. [[Sancti Spíritus (baseball)|Sancti Spíritus]], who had the best regular season record, lost in the first round. Defending champion [[La Habana (baseball)|La Habana]] were eliminated in the semifinals.
