'''Dili Institute of Technology FC''' or '''DIT FC''' is a football club of [[East Timor]] based in [[Dili]].<ref>[http://www.national-football-teams.com/club/19931/2016/Dit_Fc.html Profile on NFT]</ref> The team plays in the [[Liga Futebol Amadora]]. They reached the [[2016 Taça 12 de Novembro]] semi-finals before they lost 1-2 by the champions [[AS Ponta Leste]].

[[Francisco Cosme da Souza Gama]] was their technical director.

