{{Infobox football biography |name = Habib Youssouf |image = |fullname = |birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1998|02|19|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Iconi]], Comoros |height = {{height|m=1.68}} |position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] |currentclub = [[Volcan Club de Moroni]] |clubnumber = |youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = |years1 = 2017– |clubs1 = [[Volcan Club de Moroni]] |caps1 = |goals1 = |nationalyears1 = 2016 |nationalteam1 = [[Comoros national under-20 football team|Comoros U20]] |nationalcaps1 = 2 |nationalgoals1 = 1 |nationalyears2 = 2017– |nationalteam2 = [[Comoros national football team|Comoros]] |nationalcaps2 = 5 |nationalgoals2 = 0 |club-update = 11:44, 21 May 2018 (UTC) |nationalteam-update = 11:44, 30 July 2018 (UTC) }}
'''Habib Youssouf''' (born 19 February 1998) is a [[Comoros|Comorian]] [[association football|footballer]] who currently plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Volcan Club de Moroni]].
