{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Memorial Gym | image = | location = [[Grambling]], [[Louisiana]] | coordinates = | opened = 1970 | owner = [[Grambling State University]] | operator = [[Grambling State University]] | construction_cost = | tenants = [[Grambling State Tigers]] (volleyball) | seating_capacity = 2,200 | dimensions = }}
'''Memorial Gym''' is a 2,200-seat multi-purpose [[arena]] in [[Grambling, Louisiana]].<ref>{{cite web| title=Honoring Tradition|publisher=gram.edu|url=http://www.gram.edu/aboutus/campus/historic.php|accessdate=2017-07-23}}</ref> It is home to the [[Grambling State University]] Tigers [[volleyball]] [[team]]. It was the former home of the men's and women's [[basketball]] teams.<ref>{{cite web|title=Players, friends pay tribute to Robinson|publisher=espn.com|url=http://www.espn.com/college-football/news/story?id=4926548|accessdate=2017-07-23}}</ref>
